description: For Brenn Wyson, Naked Kombat is a walk in the park. Fighting is his life, and he trains everyday in preparation for the next bout. He doesn't need to prove anything and is eager to dominate his opponent physically and sexually. Brandon Monroe has Coast Guard training and competes in triathlons. Brandon counts on his athletic body and flexible build to overcome tough boy Brynn. It's an all out head to head battle.
title: Brenn Wyson vs Brandon Monroe
